{"type": "article", "id": 55026, "title": "符合人体牙型的电动清洁器，想要帮你彻底清洁牙齿｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-07-08T22:58:46Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 3875, "name": "包装设计"}, {"id": 247, "name": "Nendo"}, {"id": 330, "name": "可口可乐"}, {"id": 51685, "name": "Azmy Anything"}, {"id": 51686, "name": "Bel& Bel Studio"}, {"id": 51687, "name": "SEVENS"}, {"id": 51688, "name": "Yu Li"}, {"id": 41284, "name": "蔡烈超"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 19, "praise_count": 223, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180708225920HOL75xf8i1PsCNY4.gif", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>CHIIZ by SEVENS</h3><p>传统牙刷很难高效清理牙齿。为此，SEVENS 团队推出了一款很实用的 CHIIZ 牙刷。它的设计非常简单，基本上就是符合人体牙型的电动清洁器，柔软的触须毛能够完全接触到全部牙齿。提供两种不同的尺寸，以便于适用于大多数嘴巴的尺寸。</p><p>CHIIZ 使用声波技术清洁牙齿，能够产生每分钟 25000 次冲击，从而保证能够有效清洁牙龈、牙缝等牙齿位置。完整充电后可持续使用 10 天，附加的无线充电装置能够支持使用最多 2 个月时间。目前，CHIIZ 在众筹平台 Kickstarter 的早鸟价格为 69 美元，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1117328500/chiiz-toothbrush-40?utm_source=www.yankodesign.com&amp;utm_medium=kickbooster&amp;utm_content=link&amp;utm_campaign=3967ec\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201807082300198Gpy6PKNBWVcsSzJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180708230019TiDLf1FGVndJmh6O.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180708230019ei0oGJLWNId7DQA1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201807082300193F9BrN4va0HMIWgp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180708230020XykiSeHjNbav8EfJ.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201807082300269XoBjEVZ2fs3HutN.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.561562\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180708230213WwHs3SFycfMENaYZ.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Massive Order by Bel&amp; Bel Studio</h3><p>巴塞罗那工作室 Bel&amp; Bel Studio 近日设计出一款踏板摩托车与 Segway 电动平衡车的混合产品 Z-scooter，让使用者可以在享受复古摩托车驾乘乐趣的同时，不对环境造成任何污染。</p><p>Z-scooter 的设计灵感源自于 Corradino D’ascanio 为 Vespa 品牌设计的踏板摩托车，从前面看上去有着强烈的意式风格，而从背后看又展现出 Segway 电动平衡车的特点。这款车专为休闲驾驶设计，最高速度可达每小时 20 公里，单次充电可最多行驶 35 公里，充电速度很快，仅需 3 至 4 小时便可充满。</p><p>此外，Z-scooter 也配备自动平衡平台，驾驶者前倾时加速，后仰减速，通过转动车把完成左转与右转动作，在静止时则可以拉下前方支座使其直立。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180708230241X4GEhtfHroPDW1k5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.695599\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180708230241gvst8wuIq6SEeX0O.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.695599\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180708230241BC6oerlpAZu3bSR5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.695599\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180708230241xY1D6Vn2Cd3897Ov.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.695599\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180708230241dFxXOmskYK1M3olt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.695599\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180708230241fJiRDZodaSYxwyOF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.695599\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180708230241jYQiUxrMv9ud6FkS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.695599\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Pig Side-table by Mario Tsai </h3><p>小猪边桌是蔡烈超为品牌 mx object 铝材系列设计的最新项目，通过探索找出铝材更多的应用可能性。作为一个边桌，小猪不仅能满足边桌的功能，而且它还增加了储存杂志和杂物的功能，小猪的外形也能够让空间充满活力。 小猪边桌有两种不同的圆筒管径 250 毫米和 200 毫米，以此来满足不同的储物容量需求。</p><p>看似要从圆筒上滑落的桌面其实非常稳定，捕捉静态到动态的一瞬间让整个边桌更具视觉冲击力和艺术价值。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180708230309gCqMD8Ip09rR7yoA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707292\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180708230309TOD9eLZg05RvFVN7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707292\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201807082303096jgUN3PbFsMnKYxa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707292\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180708230309DLZolcMC5OwEmxtS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707292\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180708230309vJ1I6LgDEyZxUzaw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.051042\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180708230309m3KTOQGgIANfcbyi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.048958\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180708230310RZBLAmP2b0QIDjKO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707292\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Assembly by Yu Li </h3><p>伦敦皇家艺术学院工业设计专业的毕业生 Yu Li 设计了一款便携式厨房 “Assembly”，涵盖了整个烹饪和餐饮过程。该装置面向家庭空间有限的千禧一代，旨在挑战传统厨房，将烹饪活动从当前的厨房中解放出来。</p><p>七合一套装包括砧板、电磁炉、两个锅具、一个餐具包、碗架和便携式盒子。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180708230333PLwincS90tjv7Jkp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180708230333yTnjQzYMStiAcp9Z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180708230333JsmGBqjL37QV1gvI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562793\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201807082303348vS1VC5t2smKhcx9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180708230334gZWupa3FvtRrTQYq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180708230334KFo8RIJCHa0ME9yN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2018/07/05/royal-college-of-art-yu-li-portable-cooking-set-design/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dezeen</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Space Between Space Collection by Azmy Anything</h3><p>出于对于太空旅行的强烈好奇心，伦敦设计工作室 Azmy Anything 受到 NASA 和太空探索的启发，推出 Space Between Space 系列家具，其中有一款酒水饮料餐具柜，借鉴了阿波罗月球车轮胎的类似人字形的花纹。它的特别之处在于只需要简单触摸一下，柜门就可以轻松向下滑动，柜体则上升至适合拿取餐具的高度。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180708230421tA82cKbaknwm9V4j.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180708230421eYIdU1VF4tD3mnHO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.685937\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180708230421PxC8cUtOGTdSy15e.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.675000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180708230422nRcQ4Oa5gsNu8ZSj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180708230422dDTScsovIVzBbA1m.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.679688\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://design-milk.com/space-between-space-a-nasa-inspired-collection-by-azmy-anything/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Design Milk</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>I LOHAS glass sparkling water by Nendo</h3><p>日本设计工作室 Nendo 新作频出，最近给日本可口可乐旗下品牌 I LOHAS 推出的苏打水设计了新瓶子，从普通版的塑料瓶换成了玻璃材质，整个瓶身和瓶子里的水一样清澈透明，品牌 logo 浅浅地印在上面，绿色的瓶盖画龙点睛。</p><p>最特别的点藏在瓶身上，做了起伏的曲线设计，它不仅是让苏打水显得更有活力，握持瓶身时手感也不错，而且放在桌面上时，随着光线的不同角度，瓶子和桌面一样都波光粼粼。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180708230500CnHl4Vq3aLImtToZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180708230500vgdQK71pIaYBumbW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707317\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201807082305001eMREmoNsa9lk3FT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180708230501zAikmQn2sXuT40a6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180708230501almjsc48ZqG0y3oi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180708230501sH51ZqYf7WNG9aty.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180708230501AU05baBjtw16C7gm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.nendo.jp/en/works/i-lohas-glass-sparkling-water/?erelease\" rel=\"nofollow\">Nendo</a></p>"}